====Alternate forms====
*[[ノ]] (no) - katakana
*[[乃]] (no) - kanji (not in use any more)


===Particle===
[[Category:Japanese particles]]
'''の''' (no)
# Indicates that the previous word has [[possessive|possession]] of the next one. In English it functions like the [[apostrophe]] or like the word "[[of]]" but with the position of possessor and possessee switched.
#:[[私]]'''の'''[[意見]] 
#::[[わたし]]'''の'''[[いけん]]
#::''[[watashi]] '''no''' [[iken]]'' 
#::my opinion
# Indicates identity (apposition): 
#:[[大統領]]のブッシュ氏 
#::[[だいとうりょう]]'''の'''ブッシュ[[し]]
#::''[[Daitōryō]] '''no''' Busshu-shi'' 
#::Mr Bush, the President
#:[[山田]]'''の'''[[馬鹿]][[野郎]]！
#::[[やまだ]]'''の'''ばかやろう！　
#::''Yamada no bakayarō!'' 
#::Yamada, you stupid jerk!
# A feminine speech sentence ending
# Indicates a question

